<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Light background for the email body */
        }
        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden; /* Ensures border-radius is applied to children */
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e53935 0%, #b71c1c 100%); /* Red gradient */
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .header p {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e53935; /* Primary red button color */
            color: white !important; /* Ensure the link text is white */
            padding: 14px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px; /* Slightly more rounded like your example */
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #b71c1c; /* Darker red on hover */
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background: #fff3e0; /* Lighter warning background */
            border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; /* Orange left border */
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background: #ffebee; /* Light red/pink security background */
            border-left: 4px solid #ef5350; /* Red left border */
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 12px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Password Reset</h1>
            <p>School Base</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello {{ name }},</h2>
            
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your <b>School Base</b> account. Click the button below to proceed.</p>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{ resetLink }}" class="button">
                    Reset My Password
                </a>
            </div>

            <p>This link will take you to a secure page where you can set a new password. For security reasons, the link will only be active for 1 hour.</p>
            
            <div class="expiry-notice">
                <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> The reset link will expire on **{{ resetTokenExpiry }}**.
            </div>
            
            <p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure.</p>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <strong>Security Tip:</strong> **School Base** will never ask for your password.
            </div>
            
            <p>Need help? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@openschoolportal.com" style="color: #e53935; text-decoration: none;">support@openschoolportal.com</a></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{ currentYear }} School Base. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>